OL,7,FSince her daughter's death, Phyllis
OL,8,FDaly has devoted her life to driving
OL,9,Fchange. Today, ITV News joined Phyllis
OL,10,Fand the mothers of Kiena and Chloe as
OL,11,Fthey lobbied the government directly.
OL,13,FIn a meeting with Jess Phillips, the
OL,14,FMinister for Safeguarding and Violence
OL,15,Fagainst Women they told her the
OL,16,Fprofessionals "failed to support"
OL,17,Ftheir daughters.
OL,19,FEach of their stories are traumatic.
OL,20,FIn each case, the authorities had been
OL,21,Fmade aware of claims of abuse.
