OL,7,FJessie Laverack
OL,9,FJessie was a hugely talented
OL,10,Fhairdresser; described by her family
OL,11,Fas "vibrant and artistic".
OL,13,FHer inquest heard of the years of
OL,14,F"horrific" abuse she endured.
OL,16,FAlthough Jessie's boyfriend denied the
OL,17,Fallegations and was never convicted,
OL,18,Fher inquest was the first time a
OL,19,Fcoroner in the UK explicitly linked
OL,20,Fsuicide to domestic abuse.
