OL,7,FIt took her mother Phyllis almost five
OL,8,Fyears to get authorities to establish
OL,9,Fa link between domestic abuse and
OL,10,Fsuicide. Now she wants authorities to
OL,11,Fact on it, before women feel there is
OL,12,Fno other way out.
OL,14,FShe told ITV News: "I can't move on,
OL,15,Fbecause I have to keep fighting. Not
OL,16,Ffor my Jessie, because my Jessie is
OL,17,Fnot here any more, but for all them
OL,18,Fother Jessies and women and people out
OL,19,Fthere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
