OL,7,F"I have grandchildren, and I want them
OL,8,Fto be safe. I want them to feel the
OL,9,Fworld is a safer place."
OL,11,FShe added: "I have to hope, I have to
OL,12,Ftry and I will keep trying because
OL,13,Fthat's the only thing I have left to
OL,14,Fdo for her.
OL,16,F"She wanted to live, but she just
OL,17,Fdidn't want to live that life of
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse, and that's the
OL,19,Fdifference."
OL,21,FKiena Dawes
