OL,7,F"I fought long. I went through pain no
OL,8,Fone could imagine. I was murdered.
OL,9,FRyan Wellings killed me," read the
OL,10,Fsuicide note from Kiena Dawes.
OL,12,FA new mum, who adored her nine-month-
OL,13,Fold daughter and would do anything to
OL,14,Fprotect her.
OL,16,FHer family knew that Kiena was driven
OL,17,Fto suicide after years of domestic
OL,18,Fviolence. And for the first time in
OL,19,FEngland, the law recognised this too.
