OL,7,FHer former partner Ryan Wellings
OL,8,Fbecame the first defendant in England
OL,9,Fto face trial for unlawful killing,
OL,10,Fafter Kiena's suicide following
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,13,FWellings was sentenced to six and a
OL,14,Fhalf years in prison for controlling
OL,15,Fand coercive behaviour and assault but
OL,16,Fwas cleared of her manslaughter.
OL,18,FKiena's mother, Angela Dawes, still
OL,19,Fvisibly traumatised by her daughter's
OL,20,Fsudden death, sat alongside Phyllis as
OL,21,Fthey pleaded for change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
