OL,7,F"She reached out and she had a baby in
OL,8,Fher tummy, she reached out when that
OL,9,Fbaby was born," Angela said.
OL,11,F"A tiny little baby in that flat
OL,12,Fwitnessing time and time again,
OL,13,FWellings, doing that to Kiena."
OL,15,FShe continued: "I have to live the
OL,16,Frest of my life knowing that I kept
OL,17,Fsaying to my daughter 'the police will
OL,18,Fprotect you, it's okay, you're doing
OL,19,Fthe right thing'.
OL,21,F"They let her down."
