OL,7,FChloe had reported Marc Masterton for
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse and gave a two-hour
OL,9,Fvideo submission to police that led to
OL,10,Fthe 26-year-old's conviction for
OL,11,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for 41 months.
OL,15,F"My whole life's changed. It will
OL,16,Fnever go back to the same as it was
OL,17,Fbefore. It's just not the same
OL,18,Fanymore," Sharon told me.
OL,20,F"Losing your child... You just can't
OL,21,Fgo back from that."
