OL,7,FSharon now wants a separate charge of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter by coercive control for
OL,9,Foffenders whose victims kill
OL,10,Fthemselves as a result of domestic
OL,11,Fabuse.
OL,13,FChloe Holland's mother, Sharon, told
OL,14,FITV News "with what's happened,
OL,15,Fsometimes it's hard to believe there
OL,16,Fis going to be change"
