OL,7,F"I still feel angry. And with what's
OL,8,Fhappened, sometimes it's hard to
OL,9,Fbelieve there is going to be change.
OL,10,FAll you can do is look forward and
OL,11,Fhope that future something will change
OL,12,Fand this stops happening."
OL,14,FSharon added: "I would like to see the
OL,15,Fpolice trained a lot more to
