OL,7,FShe has since set up an online
OL,8,Fcampaign group called "Her Name Was
OL,9,FChloe Holland" for families who have
OL,10,Flost their loved ones after they took
OL,11,Ftheir own life following being
OL,12,Fdomestically abused.
OL,14,FToday's meeting at the Home Office
OL,15,Fcomes as new figures show that for the
OL,16,Fsecond consecutive year, more victims
OL,17,Fof domestic abuse are taking their own
OL,18,Flives than being killed by their
OL,19,Fpartner or former partner.
