OL,3,CMothers of three women who died by
OL,4,Csuicide after domestic abuse call for
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FBetween April 2023 and March 2024,
OL,8,Fthere were 262 deaths, of which 98
OL,9,Fwere suspected suicide following
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse; 80 a killing by a
OL,11,Fcurrent or ex-partner; 39 by another
OL,12,Fadult relative; 28 unexpected deaths;
OL,13,F11 child deaths and six classified as
OL,14,Fother.
OL,16,FThis will make uncomfortable reading
OL,17,Ffor Jess Phillips, a politician who
OL,18,Fhas dedicated her working life to
OL,19,Ffighting for women and girls who have
OL,20,Fsuffered violence at the hands of men.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
