OL,7,FMinutes after meeting these three
OL,8,Fgrieving mothers, she told ITV News:
OL,9,F"I am impatient for change.
OL,11,F"But what I don't want people to think
OL,12,Fis that you can overhaul systems that
OL,13,Fhave existed for hundreds of years,
OL,14,Fwhether it's a judicial system, our
OL,15,Fjustice system, our criminal system,
OL,16,Flike so many things, that you can
OL,17,Foverturn it in nine months' time.
OL,19,F"Systematic change is going to take a
OL,20,Flong time. Do I find that frustrating?
OL,21,FYes."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
