OL,7,F'I am impatient for change,' says Jess
OL,8,FPhillips
OL,10,FThese women are sick of hearing that
OL,11,Flessons have been learned, sick of
OL,12,Fhearing that changes are needed.
OL,14,FThey want real action; law changes and
OL,15,Fproper protection for victims of
OL,16,Fdomestic abuse within the police,
OL,17,Fambulance service, NHS, social
OL,18,Fservices and the criminal justice
OL,19,Fsystem. And they want the courts given
OL,20,Fgreater powers so sentences will act
OL,21,Fas a deterrent rather than a let off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
