OL,7,FFor many families, fighting for change
OL,8,Fseems fruitless. They have lost their
OL,9,Floved ones and they are broken.
OL,11,FFor others, it is the fight that keeps
OL,12,Fthem going.
OL,14,FEither way, it seems so cruel that we
OL,15,Fare relying on the pain of grieving
OL,16,Ffamilies to orchestrate genuine change.
